track_notes:
Classif E . Easy path from Colla dei Termini 2000 m. 
From Ormea narrow but asphalted road till Cascine 1200 m . 
You can follow the dusty road till your car start to cry. 
The best choice is to stop about 1500 m and enjoy the nice walk ( or if you had mountain byke ) till the Colla .
